extern:

here you can stage external packages, see [1].

for example
git clone git://tool.em.cs.uni-frankfurt.de/git/gnucap-bsim --branch master extern/bsim
cd !$; ./autogen.sh; cd -
./configure
make install

or just (untested)
tar -xf some_bsim_tarball -C extern/bsim --strip-components 1
# no autogen
./configure ...

this is under construction also for spice3f5
results may vary, please report trouble

[1] http://www.gnu.org/software/automake/manual/html_node/Subpackages.html
